Olympus01BCE@مصرأم الدنيا

Log-in to Server 2k12
Firewall:
Click on tools(top menu): Windows Firewall and Advanced Security
	Click on Windows Firewall Properties in the bottom of Overview
	Block all inbound traffic

Open Internet Explorer:
	Go to options, disable enhanced security

Click on Server Manager icon:
	It is pinned to the taskbar
	if not, search for it
Click on tools(top menu): Computer Management
Click on: Local users and groups (on the left pane)
click on: Users>>Administrator
	Right click Administrator: set password
OR
Create a new user: right click anywhere and create user
	add user name, full name, and password
	make user change password next log on
Disable Administrator: right click on it > properties > disable

Disable remote desktop
